skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my roadmap
des: With the roadmap skill user could create and update roadmap for their specific goals. It’s like a planner for your life goals ex :if user has an exam then they could add a roadmap as first I will finish notes then the books then library books and so on. User can create, update insert or delete any items in roadmaps table. All data is stored in dynamo DB so the data will be persistent
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
